OL,3,CUK bans fake reviews and hidden online
OL,4,Cshopping fees under new law
OL,6,FFake reviews and so-called drip
OL,7,Fpricing for online shopping are banned
OL,8,Funder a new law that comes into force
OL,9,Ffrom Sunday.
OL,11,FAdministration fees and ticking
OL,12,Fbooking fees must now be included in
OL,13,Fthe headline price but the law does
OL,14,Fnot cover optional fees such as
OL,15,Fairline seats and baggage upgrades for
OL,16,Fflights.
OL,18,FGoing forward, online platforms will,
OL,19,Fby law, have to take steps to prevent
OL,20,Fand remove fake consumer reviews from
OL,21,Ftheir websites.
