OL,4,Cshopping fees under new law
OL,6,FConsumers spend #2.2 billion on hidden
OL,7,Ffees every year, according to the
OL,8,FDepartment for Business and Trade.
OL,10,FJustin Madders, minister for
OL,11,Fcompetition and markets, said: "From
OL,12,Ftoday consumers can confidently make
OL,13,Fpurchases knowing they are protected
OL,14,Fagainst fake reviews and dripped
OL,15,Fpricing.
